  <body>
    <div style="basic">
        <p begin="00:00:00.3" end="00:00:04.6" tts:direction="ltr">Hi, Data 2,100 Concur enrollment students.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:04.6" end="00:00:08.4" tts:direction="ltr">Thank you so much for joining me this
<br/>spring semester.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:08.4" end="00:00:10.4" tts:direction="ltr">My name is Reagan Sigurd.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:10.4" end="00:00:13.6" tts:direction="ltr">I'm going to orient you a little bit to
<br/>where this class comes from.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:13.6" end="00:00:15.7" tts:direction="ltr">This is a fully asynchronous,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:15.7" end="00:00:20.9" tts:direction="ltr">meaning there's not specific times that we
<br/>need course full of videos,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:20.9" end="00:00:25" tts:direction="ltr">full of resources to help you progress
<br/>through Data 2,100,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:25" end="00:00:27.5" tts:direction="ltr">data and information in Business.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:27.5" end="00:00:30.2" tts:direction="ltr">So let's talk about what is this class.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:30.2" end="00:00:32.4" tts:direction="ltr">Well, first off, a little hello.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:32.4" end="00:00:33.7" tts:direction="ltr">So as I said,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:33.7" end="00:00:35" tts:direction="ltr">my name is Regan Siggd.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:35" end="00:00:36.5" tts:direction="ltr">I'm an assistant professor in</p>
        <p begin="00:00:36.5" end="00:00:39.3" tts:direction="ltr">the data analytics and Information systems
<br/>department.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:39.3" end="00:00:42.1" tts:direction="ltr">There is my email address and</p>
        <p begin="00:00:42.1" end="00:00:45.1" tts:direction="ltr">office hours are listed on the homepage of
<br/>Canvas.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:45.1" end="00:00:50.4" tts:direction="ltr">I'm also more than happy to meet anytime
<br/>that you need help.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:50.4" end="00:00:52.4" tts:direction="ltr">Please just send me an email and we'll</p>
        <p begin="00:00:52.4" end="00:00:54.5" tts:direction="ltr">schedule a time that we can meet and chat.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:54.5" end="00:01:00.3" tts:direction="ltr">I'm more than willing to be a resource to
<br/>you at any point during this course.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:00.3" end="00:01:04.6" tts:direction="ltr">That being said, I do recognize that you
<br/>are high school students,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:04.6" end="00:01:06.3" tts:direction="ltr">and so sometimes meeting in</p>
        <p begin="00:01:06.3" end="00:01:07.9" tts:direction="ltr">the traditional eight to five schedule</p>
        <p begin="00:01:07.9" end="00:01:09.8" tts:direction="ltr">doesn't work for you, and that's just
<br/>fine.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:09.8" end="00:01:13.3" tts:direction="ltr">I'm happy to meet outside of that if that
<br/>works better for you.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:13.3" end="00:01:17.6" tts:direction="ltr">Um, so let's talk a little bit about where
<br/>this class comes from,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:17.6" end="00:01:20.2" tts:direction="ltr">and I'll talk a little bit more about
<br/>myself as well.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:20.2" end="00:01:21.1" tts:direction="ltr">So here we have a picture of</p>
        <p begin="00:01:21.1" end="00:01:25" tts:direction="ltr">the Wellsville Mountains and beautiful
<br/>Cache Valley, Utah.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:25" end="00:01:29.5" tts:direction="ltr">So this class is based at Utah State
<br/>University's Logan campus,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:29.5" end="00:01:30.8" tts:direction="ltr">which is in Cache Valley,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:30.8" end="00:01:32.7" tts:direction="ltr">the northern part of the state.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:32.7" end="00:01:35.4" tts:direction="ltr">I live up here, I live on a little funny
<br/>farm,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:35.4" end="00:01:38.8" tts:direction="ltr">recently got into horses, loving that.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:38.8" end="00:01:41.9" tts:direction="ltr">I have, as I said, a little funny farm.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:41.9" end="00:01:44.9" tts:direction="ltr">I love agriculture. I love being outside.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:44.9" end="00:01:47.7" tts:direction="ltr">And so I live here in Cache Valley.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:47.7" end="00:01:50" tts:direction="ltr">So this class is coming to you from Cache
