        <p begin="00:02:41.3" end="00:02:45" tts:direction="ltr">So we are a part of the Don and Huntman
<br/>School of Business and specifically,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:45" end="00:02:47.9" tts:direction="ltr">there are departments within a college.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:47.9" end="00:02:51.4" tts:direction="ltr">And I'm in the data Analytics and
