        <p begin="00:02:51.4" end="00:02:54.4" tts:direction="ltr">We say DAIS for short,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:54.4" end="00:02:56.4" tts:direction="ltr">and you can understand why.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:56.4" end="00:02:59.5" tts:direction="ltr">And our department, I mean,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:59.5" end="00:03:01.7" tts:direction="ltr">I am biased in this, definitely,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:01.7" end="00:03:06.7" tts:direction="ltr">but we have fantastic faculty whom I am so
<br/>privileged to work with,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:06.7" end="00:03:10.2" tts:direction="ltr">and we have a sole focus on student
<br/>success.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:10.2" end="00:03:13.4" tts:direction="ltr">So we have our Analytics solution Center,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:13.4" end="00:03:15.2" tts:direction="ltr">which is a part of our department,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:15.2" end="00:03:18.2" tts:direction="ltr">and we contract with real organizations,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:18.2" end="00:03:21.2" tts:direction="ltr">and they give us data and a problem to
