        <p begin="00:03:57.9" end="00:04:00.9" tts:direction="ltr">So I'll be announcing that you're more
<br/>than welcome to come up.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:00.9" end="00:04:05.8" tts:direction="ltr">But the Hackathon, It's basically you work
