        <p begin="00:04:25.3" end="00:04:29.8" tts:direction="ltr">really devoted time and we want you to put
<br/>together projects.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:29.8" end="00:04:34.5" tts:direction="ltr">So I hope you're seeing that we have these
